{"tid":128761,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[多圖有教學] 今日好開心，女朋友整朱古力甜品我食……","createTime":"2017-02-21T05:37:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-21T17:03:45.000Z","uid":63452,"like":11,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3dbfa2b89d51f9b3418d055a1a4ec2ec87448d2b","tid":128761,"uid":63452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T05:37:51.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n女朋友一向知我鍾意食甜品<br />\n咁啱佢係網上面見到原來有微波爐就整到嘅甜品<br />\n(聽落唔難整，應該冇伏啦我諗)<br />\n佢就襯今日我溫書溫到肚餓嘅提議整俾我食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n材料好簡單：就係棉花糖同黑朱古力<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/21/131848_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F21%2F131848_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=eb330285&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁佢就以為好簡單啦，將啲嘢擺埋一齊去叮就得<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/21/132013_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg/132013_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b 8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F21%2F132013_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg%2F132013_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b%208f5ae22.jpg&h=350e4b6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁我就坐埋一邊等食女朋友&hellip;舊甜品啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知我又衰好奇<br />\n擰轉身望下個微波爐叮成點喎&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">咦喂，舊嘢脹緊嘅屌？！</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/25NHOMv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F25NHOMv.jpg&h=9adad6d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁唔緊要啦，女朋友笑曬口咁興奮等舊嘢生成<br />\n我就無出聲，靜靜地等食<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點知&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2MEL6MG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2MEL6MG.jpg&h=f85d5307&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁佢見到成舊屎咁，都知唔對路<br />\n就話想拎隻叉搞搞佢，試圖補救一下個賣相<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n話口未完，舊嘢就變成咁&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w010azo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw010azo.jpg&h=28e0e517&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n結果女朋友喊曬口咁樣，話自己冇用整舊屎出嚟<br />\n我就唯有梗硬食曬碟嘢佢&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b8c23a06ae6eaff9326b774c6c33f23acb211ec","tid":128761,"uid":52271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T05:40:52.000Z","msg":"冇爆炸，執返條命<br />\n食屎已經係好結果"},{"pid":"4ec3ee5047db962cbdc81f3340b498c9c04cac74","tid":128761,"uid":63452,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T05:45:11.000Z","msg":"死圖，補返先<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3G1R818.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3G1R818.jpg&h=f9ef025f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n後續<br />\n<br />\n好在女朋友醒目<br />\n之後改良咗個方法<br />\n先分開叮熔朱古力，再叮十秒舊棉花糖<br />\n（本身一齊撈埋叮成幾分鐘，因爲朱古力唔熔）<br />\n就整返件佳作我食<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CCOs919.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCCOs919.jpg&h=7a38b2d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過下次女朋友整嘢我食<br />\n都係睇實佢好啲&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20f697106f54f2ebf20f69f569f2793b2dc3809d","tid":128761,"uid":63452,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T05:46:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/43g8Z7x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F43g8Z7x.jpg&h=08c7e0f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佳作圖2"},{"pid":"be0e8106dd96703a809bbc7f1388450ad877715d","tid":128761,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T05:51:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇爆炸，執返條命<br />\n食屎已經係好結果</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a94cc3b76de029ea5e71ec3f943290ba709340ec","tid":128761,"uid":63452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T05:54:22.000Z","msg":"between 凌晨五點食成五六舊大棉花糖都幾係嘢，依家飽到頂住個肚溫書<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52faa6dc4b94900fc258747ae6c40bee49678126","tid":128761,"uid":63452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T06:04:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c37adb0271acd8027d325f5dfaf818adaab11f41","tid":128761,"uid":34503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T06:06:20.000Z","msg":"WUBY咪教過大家用多士爐整棉花糖囉"},{"pid":"7d5540e5cd601c511aaf14359ac4529206778622","tid":128761,"uid":63452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T06:10:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>WUBY咪教過大家用多士爐整棉花糖囉</blockquote><br />\nWUBY 都好多年前下啦喎應該？"},{"pid":"536ecf34df17835ea64f804d47b1d8b183fffb0e","tid":128761,"uid":63452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T06:17:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d74a04a7bf9c314a47be696cb84e1649a37aadf","tid":128761,"uid":63452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T06:42:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f003bd07725db404f38a115b1f9ba4e43b47b276","tid":128761,"uid":63452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T07:22:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b49aeed996e1a3b755556b24eaf4670c3a67c58","tid":128761,"uid":71826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T07:36:46.000Z","msg":"女朋友？ 走喇&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"b02cf20d8996663cf079943fc21ef44a96588932","tid":128761,"uid":13747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T07:56:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>冇爆炸，執返條命<br />\n食屎已經係好結果</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/f